{"tid":133294,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"USB中左 .lnk 病毒 檔案唔見晒但仲佔空間 可以搜索到 點先見得番啲檔案","createTime":"2017-02-24T13:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T15:01:52.000Z","uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc0a60e4afc0f1046ba3f25733b85968fff77103","tid":133294,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T13:10:08.000Z","msg":"已經將所有隱藏檔案顯示但都冇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跪求幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd14756fc92eb615f2e833d9c4d95af772b5e24","tid":133294,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:26:22.000Z","msg":".lnk 唔係病毒"},{"pid":"1bcf37c2a02968a752536cf131d571a5fb2f16be","tid":133294,"uid":31515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:58:08.000Z","msg":"放去mac/linux睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061c33a4f4f5146830d3effbdfd69b64e635707c","tid":133294,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:08:26.000Z","msg":"算啦 已經fix左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nUSB實係插過唔乾淨的電腦<br />\n<br />\n個小病毒會刻意複製個 AutoRun.inf 檔在你的USB<br />\n然後利用這檔案 大量複製 類似的檔名file <br />\n例如 你本身有個file叫   &quot;ABC.pdf&quot; <br />\n你本身個file會被病毒隱藏(沒被刪除)<br />\n然後剩係會show個檔案叫 &quot;ABC.lnx&quot;<br />\n呃你以為係熟悉檔名開啟就真正中毒(maybe 檔案綁架之類)<br />\n<br />\n方法係<br />\n將所有熟悉名稱但結尾係 .lnx 的刪除 (一般防毒軟件都做到)<br />\n千萬不要開啟 .lnx 檔 會真正啟動USB毒<br />\n<br />\n將 AutoRun.inf 檔刪除 避免成為毒的寄生地方<br />\n並 開新資料夾 命名 AutoRun.inf <br />\nfake個病毒無法再自行創造 AutoRun.inf 再複製類似檔名的.lnx檔<br />\n<br />\n用普通防毒軟件check出 &quot;ckaejsmhmo.vbs&quot;<br />\n並刪除<br />\n<br />\n之後你都係會發現你本身的檔案無被刪除<br />\n但就不見失蹤 不過用搜索又會見得番晒<br />\n<br />\n0. 想初初步見番檔案<br />\n開啟&quot;cmd.exe&quot; 如果你個USB係叫 d drive<br />\n輸入&quot;dir d:\\ /a/w&quot; 注意有空白位置<br />\n係 f drive 就輸入 &quot;dir f:\\ /a/w&quot;<br />\n\\ 符號應該係 向右斜撇 的符號 連登顯示唔到錯誤變左&quot;\\&quot;<br />\n之後就檢視晒所有USB 隱藏file 所有本身正常但被病毒隱藏的file<br />\n應該仲會見到&quot;autorun.inf&quot; <br />\n部份中毒可能見到&quot;<a href=\"http://ntdelect.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fntdelect.com&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=5b431e26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ntdelect.com</a>&quot; 千萬注意非&quot;<a href=\"http://NTDETECT.COM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FNTDETECT.COM&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=6786d0a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">NTDETECT.COM</a>&quot;<br />\n都會清楚見到所有file<br />\n<br />\n1. 想初步見番檔案<br />\n第一步可以按 &quot;控制台&quot; (&quot;檢視方式&quot;選&quot;大圖示&quot;)<br />\n再選&quot;資料夾選項&quot; 然後在 &quot;檢視&quot;<br />\n拉落去見到 &quot;隱藏檔案和資料夾&quot; 入面<br />\n通常用家default選取 &quot;不顯示隱藏的檔案,資料夾和磁碟機&quot;<br />\n要改選&quot;顯示隱藏的檔案,資料夾和磁碟機&quot;<br />\n發覺還是無法看見失蹤的檔案<br />\n要再在 &quot;隱藏保護的作業系統檔案(建議選項)&quot; 取消個Tick<br />\n照舊按&quot;是&quot; 之後你會見得番晒但 半透明 隱藏狀況<br />\n係感染小病毒的後遺症<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果想直接fix左佢 (可以無視0.同1.所講的) <br />\n在防毒軟件刪除病毒檔(可能命名為&quot;ckaejsmhmo.vbs&quot;)<br />\n跟刪除所有&quot;.lnx&quot;檔 還有刪除&quot;Autorun.inf&quot;後<br />\n<br />\n首先 &quot;開始&quot; 搜索 &quot;cmd.exe&quot;命令元<br />\n開啟後<br />\n打番你USB個drive<br />\n例如個drive叫 F drive 就打 &quot;F:&quot; 然後enter<br />\n再輸入 &quot;attrib -s -r -h * /S /D&quot; (注意有空白位置)<br />\n然後enter 一段時間之後 你會見到恢復原狀<br />\n如果唔得 再試過"},{"pid":"f053887cfccd0915899925a1f132c8ccae1c1f30","tid":133294,"uid":34161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:54:25.000Z","msg":"XP 年代嘅嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb015cf623bcbc4a4a8dd0bf02dab713e791f75e","tid":133294,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T10:03:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>XP 年代嘅嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 估唔到咁on9<br />\n仲有呢種毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好彩係呢啲小學雞毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695545946a42142ed7533aefea55217147461cfa","tid":133294,"uid":64969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T15:01:52.000Z","msg":"用avg會自動del毒+fix埋 file名"}]}